            <div><opener>
                <dateline><pb/> Sunny Bank. Hirnsey Lane <lb/>22 September 1867</dateline>
                <salute>My dear Madam</salute>
            </opener>
                
                <p>I cannot tell you how
                    <?oxy_comment_start author="lindenberg" timestamp="20190930T132212+0200" comment="verärgert"?>vexed<?oxy_comment_end?>
                    I am to hear of Wilfred's
                    <?oxy_comment_start author="lindenberg" timestamp="20190930T131215+0200"?>conduct<?oxy_comment_end?>
                    in your house. I hope You and M. Lafargue will be so kind as to accept his
                    apology for his impertinence. I have let it go just as he wrote it <pb n=""/>rather than dictate any alteration in his style which, though not very
                    gracious, is I hope not
                    <?oxy_comment_start author="lindenberg" timestamp="20190930T132936+0200" comment="eingefügt von mir, da nicht transkribiert: unaufrichtig"?>insincere<?oxy_comment_end?></p>
                <p>I remain</p>
                <p>My dear Madam</p>
                <p>Yours very truly</p>
                <p>C. D. Collet.</p>
                <p/>
                <p/>
                <p>Dr. Marx.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
